snippet.title: Press Pass Latino
snippet.description:
Press Pass Latino covers news, entertainment, beauty, fashion and lifestyle stories from an angle that's relevant to the Generation Y Hispanic which is easy for us because that's exactly who our staff is made up of. 

We strive to provide you a multimedia press pass and let you discover a fresh and interesting point of view for every story. 

Visit us at www.presspasslatino.com
